Summary: 4 odd lights caught in photo by accident
divs: Sighting DetailsA friend posts pics of scenery everyday I always look at them and like them but one particular one caught my eye as I saw four distinct lights of orb shape in the pic. I zoomed in and was astonished as to what I saw . I am a paranormal investigator and this immediately seemed odd with me so I shared it with a team member and he used crude software and enhanced the pics and even this low quality is still unexplainable to me . My friend said she didn't see anything apparent or hear anything but that it has just begun to rain and she was standing outside .
